2026-05-15T07:15:41.1065451Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T07:15:41.1066167Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T07:15:41.1066775Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T07:15:41.1067382Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T07:15:41.1068381Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T07:15:41.1069112Z 231            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T07:15:41.1069859Z 232            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-15T07:15:41.1070513Z 233            preserve via tools:node="merge".
