2026-05-15T07:15:41.4798648Z 249            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4798987Z 250            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4799317Z 251            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4799652Z 252            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4799862Z 253            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4800230Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4800560Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4800870Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4801197Z 257            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-15T07:15:41.4801394Z 258            preserve via tools:node="merge".
